column4: NSLOCTEXT("[8A602A1B4757E3E351BE1386307262A9]", "9007163D41DE23F53A14D791DF094BF0", "Excuse me... I want to go to the city. Ribbit!")
NSLOCTEXT("[8A602A1B4757E3E351BE1386307262A9]", "2BA7E96046B008F8DF484A973C04CB07", "I wanna fight at the Arena. It seems like we, the Gekomon Tribe,")
NSLOCTEXT("[8A602A1B4757E3E351BE1386307262A9]", "511300C5492904BC0CF24D8D7E713ECE", "Are looked down upon as country Digimon. Ribbit.")
NSLOCTEXT("[8A602A1B4757E3E351BE1386307262A9]", "A2843E1E4ED73505943DBB98C0C18EE2", "Yeah, we\'re from the country, but we have our pride too!")
NSLOCTEXT("[8A602A1B4757E3E351BE1386307262A9]", "8C4F9B9A4427AD51A83EBCA233C2E306", "I see how you feel. Then, try it. Good luck!")
